# USA Student Visa Checklist

## Documents Required
- Passport (valid min. 6 months)
- I-20 form from university
- SEVIS payment receipt
- DS-160 confirmation
- Visa appointment confirmation
- Financial documents (bank statements, CA report)
- Academic documents (marksheets, transcripts)
- Passport-size photos (as per US visa specs)

## Interview Preparation
- Why this university?
- Future plans?
- Who is sponsoring you?
- Why not study in India?

## Tips
- Be confident, short & clear
- Carry originals + photocopies
